        <h2 class="bw-modular__title" style="font-size:clamp(24px, 3vw, 34px);">Premium kitchens work best when the planning is as strong as the visual finish</h2>
        <p class="bw-modular__copy">A good modular kitchen should feel refined on day one and still work smoothly years later. That means the design conversation has to cover layout, work zones, storage habits, material durability, and how the kitchen connects to the rest of the home.</p>
